high_descs: Turn around and walk into the large room, passing the white dining table, then turn left as the wall opens to the small coffee table.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Go further into the large room towards the opposite end of the coffee table to the large TV stand with a book on it.
Slice the potato on the table.
Go back to where you started, going past the white dining table into the kitchen area, approaching the sink.
Place the knife inside the sink.
Return to the TV stand where you sliced the potato.
Pick up one slice of the potato.
Return to the kitchen area, this time looking to the microwave opposite the sink.
Use the microwave on the potato slice and remove it.
Turn back towards the sink you put the knife in.
Place the potato slice in the sink next to the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved potato slice inside a kitchen sink.

high_descs: Turn around go pass the dining table, turn left to the coffee table.
Pick up the knife from the coffee table.
Go to the TV stand in front of the sofa.
Slice the potato on the TV stand.
Head to the sink beside the fridge.
Place the knife in the sink beside the fridge.
Head back to the TV stand.
Pick up a slice of potato from the front end.
Head back to the sink and turn around to the red microwave.
Place the potato slice in the microwave, heat it, and pick it back up.
Turn around to the sink.
Place the potato slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated slice of potato in the sink.

TAKE A PIECE OF POTATO FROM THE TV STAND
TURN TWO RIGHT TO REACH MICROWAVE OVEN
KEEP THE POTATO INSIDE THE OVEN AND TAKE IT OUT AFTER SOMETIME
TURN AROUND TOWARDS THE SINK
KEEP THE POTATO IN THE SINK
anns.task_desc: TO HEAT THE POTATO IN OVEN KEEP IN SINK
